new Bias(source: "http://carolinapublicpress.org/", factuality: "HIGH", biasType: "Left-Center Bias", notes: "Carolina Public Press is North Carolinas first online nonprofit news organization to be devoted to original; enterprise-level; in-depth and investigative journalism in the public interest. Its also the only news organization in Western North Carolina to have credentialed journalists working in Raleigh as part of the Capitol Press Corps reporting on the N.C. General Assembly. Carolina Public Press has a left of center bias in reporting and political affiliation. Sources all information well. (1/24/2017) Updated (4/7/2017)"),
