new Bias(source: "http://ctj.org/", factuality: "HIGH", biasType: "Left-Center Bias", notes: "Citizens for Tax Justice is a progressive Washington; D.C.-based advocacy and lobbying think tank founded in 1979.CTJs work focuses primarily on federal tax policy. CTJ is generally considered to be a left-wing organization;but its research has also been cited by Republicanpoliticiansand right-wing tax reform organizations when favorable to their policies. CTJ is usually well sourced to credible information and uses minimal loaded words. Favors liberal economic policy. (9/17/2016)"),
