new Bias(source: "http://crosscut.com/", factuality: "HIGH", biasType: "Left-Center Bias", notes: "Crosscut.com is a nonprofit; online newspaper based in Seattle; Washington; United States. Crosscuts stated purpose is to produce journalism in the public interest.Its content is mainly news analysis rather than breaking news like other online newspapers or blogs. Most articles are well sourced. There is slight use of loaded words that lean left. (3/7/2017)"),
