new Bias(source: "http://uspoln.com", factuality: "N/A", biasType: "Satire", notes: "According to their website; USPOLN is a US Political News and hybrid News/Satire platform on the web.Its About Us pagesaysits content may include information from sources that may or may not be reliable and facts that dont necessarily exist and these articles should be considered satirical and any and all quotes attributed to actual people complete and total baloney. (2/27/2017) Updated (7/7/2017)"),
